'''Alison Edith Hilda Drummond''' (22 January 1903&ndash;3 July 1984) was a New Zealand farmer, writer, historian and editor. She was born in [[Waitekauri]], [[Thames/Coromandel]], [[New Zealand]] on 22 January 1903.<ref name="DNZB Drummond">{{DNZB|title=Alison Edith Hilda Drummond|first= Esther|last= Irving|id=5d26|accessdate=6 February 2012}}</ref>

